      "content": "look i'm not trying to be difficult but i really cant go. i asked my neighbor and they said i could just take some more of the salbutamol and maybe some ibuprofen to help with the inflammation? if i just take a higher dose of the inhaler and some anti-inflammatories it should settle it down without a huge trip to the hospital right?",
